text-unit.text:
An alternative solution may be to set large equations into two-column-wide tables or figures. An experimental package for setting equations that span two columns, asmewide.sty, can be loaded as well, but that code may require hand-fitting around figures, tables, and page breaks. See the examples in [



  11



].

