(3) 𝐹 → = 𝑚 𝑎 → or F → = 𝑚 a → or 𝐅 = 𝑚 𝐚 or F → = 𝑚 a →
\begin {equation}\label {eqn:dw} \vec {F} = m \vec {a} \quad \textrm {or}\quad \vec {\mathrm {F}} = m \vec {\mathrm {a}} \quad \textrm {or}\quad \mathbf {F} = m \mathbf {a} \quad \textrm {or}\quad \vec {\mathsf {F}} = m \vec {\mathsf {a}}\end {equation}
